Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,欢迎加入OCR小组 qq群906722936 字幕优先发布于群内 字幕广告招租 商业合作Q:1585235535
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.94,0:00:20.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,《比利小子》前情提要\N{\rYUANWEN}Previously, on Billy the Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.19,0:00:22.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我跟你一个好朋友一起骑马放牛\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm ridin'with a good friend of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.19,0:00:24.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-你认识杰西吗 -我当然认识\N{\rYUANWEN}You know Jesse? - Sure I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.69,0:00:26.36,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我决不离开\N{\rYUANWEN}- I will never leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.95,0:00:29.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不 不 不\N{\rYUANWEN}No! No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.20,0:00:30.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你要逮捕我\N{\rYUANWEN}You're arrestin' me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.70,0:00:32.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,布雷迪治安官只想和你谈谈\N{\rYUANWEN}Sheriff Brady just wants to talk to ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.70,0:00:36.08,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是我们的老板 墨菲市长让我过去的\N{\rYUANWEN}Major Murphy, our boss, told me to go up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.08,0:00:37.95,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我别无选择 只能开枪\N{\rYUANWEN}I had no alternative but to shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.96,0:00:39.21,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以算是正当防卫\N{\rYUANWEN}So it was self- defense?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.21,0:00:40.96,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他也许会离开一段时间\N{\rYUANWEN}Maybe he goes away for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.96,0:00:43.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,重新学习 以执法者的身份回归\N{\rYUANWEN}Gets re- educated. Comes back out the other side as a lawman.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.92,0:00:46.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,比利和德尔·托博斯科的女儿杜尔西内亚\N{\rYUANWEN}Billy got real friendly with Del Tobosco's daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.92,0:00:48.05,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,关系很好\N{\rYUANWEN}Dulcinea.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.26,0:00:52.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,卡特隆先生如果想要我的财产\N{\rYUANWEN}If Mr. Catron wants my belongings,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.22,0:00:55.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我的牛 马 都可以给他\N{\rYUANWEN}everything, my horses, my cattle he can have them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.22,0:00:57.01,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,让开\N{\rYUANWEN}Get out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.02,0:00:58.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你们都是一群魔鬼\N{\rYUANWEN}Devils, all of you! -
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.27,0:01:01.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们杀了所有人 比利\N{\rYUANWEN}They killed everyone, Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.90,0:01:03.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,杀了我全家\N{\rYUANWEN}My whole family.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.11,0:01:06.86,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,其中一个持枪歹徒假扮成了你 比利\N{\rYUANWEN}One of the gunmen pretended to be you, Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.86,0:01:09.32,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我会为你家人报仇的 我发誓\N{\rYUANWEN}I will avenge your family's death, I swear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.32,0:01:11.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这里为什么这么多人\N{\rYUANWEN}Why are all these men here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.28,0:01:12.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,因为我们要接管这个镇了\N{\rYUANWEN}Because we're gonna take over the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.99,0:01:15.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,林肯县人民早已厌倦了没有王法\N{\rYUANWEN}The people of Lincoln are tired of the lawlessness...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.12,0:01:16.83,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,一片混乱的世界\N{\rYUANWEN}...and the chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.91,0:01:21.41,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们想要改变 是时候了\N{\rYUANWEN}They want change. Now is the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.42,0:01:23.42,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我之前不理解你为什么要开战\N{\rYUANWEN}I told you I didn't understand why you needed to go to war.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.42,0:01:25.17,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,现在理解了\N{\rYUANWEN}Now I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.17,0:01:26.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,胡安·帕特隆在很多人心中\N{\rYUANWEN}Most of you will also know Juan Patron
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.84,0:01:28.96,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,都是西班牙裔社区的领导者\N{\rYUANWEN}as a leading member of the Hispanic community.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.96,0:01:30.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,地位十分重要\N{\rYUANWEN}He's very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.72,0:01:31.34,YUANWEN,,0,0,0,,It's an honor, Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.93,0:01:33.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这是约翰·威尔逊法官 比利\N{\rYUANWEN}This is Judge John Wilson, Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.43,0:01:35.01,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,就是他签发了约翰·汤斯顿谋杀凶手的\N{\rYUANWEN}It was he who issued the warrant for the arrest
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.01,0:01:37.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,逮捕令\N{\rYUANWEN}of those responsible for John Tunstall's murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.10,0:01:38.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,看来还是有人站我们这边的\N{\rYUANWEN}So after all, there are people on our side.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.93,0:01:40.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,麦克斯文先生 你需要配枪吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Mr. McSween, would you like a gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.27,0:01:42.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我做了这么久的牧师早已立誓\N{\rYUANWEN}I was a pastor all these years and Ive sworn off
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:43.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不再用枪了\N{\rYUANWEN}ever using a gun myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.73,0:01:44.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你好 曼纽拉\N{\rYUANWEN}Hola, Manuela.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.94,0:01:47.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这位是杜尔西内亚·德尔·托博斯科女士\N{\rYUANWEN}This is Senorita Dulcinea Del Tobosco.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.98,0:01:49.44,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,她需要一个安全之暂避\N{\rYUANWEN}She needs somewhere safe to hole up for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.44,0:01:51.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不知能否住你这里\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm hoping she can stay here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.15,0:01:52.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,卡特隆先生刚刚任命了\N{\rYUANWEN}Mr. Catron has just appointed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.40,0:01:54.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,林肯县的新任治安官\N{\rYUANWEN}a new sheriff in Lincoln County.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.70,0:01:57.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他誓要把每一个不法分子和枪手\N{\rYUANWEN}A sheriff who's pledged to drive each and every gunman
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.99,0:02:02.79,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,赶出这片土地 恢复法律和秩序\N{\rYUANWEN}and outlaw out of this territory and restore law and order.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.79,0:02:05.21,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我建议你和他合作\N{\rYUANWEN}I suggest you co- operate with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.21,0:02:07.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你和我 是合作伙伴\N{\rYUANWEN}You and me, we're partners here
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.92,0:02:11.80,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我恨不得现在就把\N{\rYUANWEN}and all I want is nothing more
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.80,0:02:14.01,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那个该死的比利小子\N{\rYUANWEN}than to see that Billy the fuckin' Kid
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.01,0:02:15.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,送上绞刑架\N{\rYUANWEN}hangin'on the end of a rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.13,0:03:38.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,杰西\N{\rYUANWEN}Jesse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.64,0:03:40.80,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,请坐吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Take a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.93,0:03:46.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,最近怎么样\N{\rYUANWEN}Hw you gettin' on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.98,0:03:49.56,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,还行吧\N{\rYUANWEN}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.56,0:03:51.52,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,忙着任命副手\N{\rYUANWEN}Sworn in my deputies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.52,0:03:53.36,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,熟悉新的职责\N{\rYUANWEN}Gettin'to know my way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.36,0:03:55.32,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你呢 找到比利了吗\N{\rYUANWEN}What about you? You any closer to findin'Billy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.15,0:03:59.36,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,在努力了 找到些线索\N{\rYUANWEN}Tryin". Had some leads.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.36,0:04:01.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他应该把老巢撤了很远\N{\rYUANWEN}Reckon he pulled his camp way back, out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.45,0:04:03.33,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你觉得他是想干什么\N{\rYUANWEN}What do you think he's planning to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.33,0:04:06.50,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,想想他最不可能做什么\N{\rYUANWEN}Think about the most unlikely thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.50,0:04:07.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,也许就是他的一下计划\N{\rYUANWEN}that's probably what he'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.46,0:04:10.25,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,比如呢\N{\rYUANWEN}Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.25,0:04:12.46,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他一直处于守势 被动挨打\N{\rYUANWEN}He's been on the defensive. He's reacting to things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.46,0:04:14.00,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,以我对他的了解\N{\rYUANWEN}My guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:16.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他宁愿主动出击\N{\rYUANWEN}He'd rather be on the offense.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.30,0:04:18.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不然他知道自己会被围剿殆尽\N{\rYUANWEN}Otherwise, he knows he's going to get hunted down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.01,0:04:21.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,因此 我们最好保持警惕\N{\rYUANWEN}We best be vigilant, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.47,0:04:27.14,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这样吧 我可以给你分点人手\N{\rYUANWEN}You know what? Ican spare you some of my men
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.14,0:04:28.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,一起追捕他\N{\rYUANWEN}to help with your hunt for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.02,0:04:31.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们要保证对他的压制\N{\rYUANWEN}Got to keep the pressure on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.11,0:04:35.44,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢 很感谢\N{\rYUANWEN}Thanks. Appreciate that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.49,0:04:40.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但不得不说 看你戴着治安官警徽的样子\N{\rYUANWEN}I gotta say, it's strange seeing you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.28,0:04:42.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,感觉很奇怪\N{\rYUANWEN}with that sheriff's badge on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.54,0:04:53.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我已经不是之前那个我了 杰西\N{\rYUANWEN}Things were very different back then, Jesse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.88,0:04:56.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我当时很迷失 HERI\N{\rYUANWEN}I was a lost soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.30,0:04:58.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,找不到方向\N{\rYUANWEN}Didn't know which way to turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.10,0:05:05.14,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你有过这种感觉吗\N{\rYUANWEN}You ever felt that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.43,0:05:12.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,应该没有过 治安官\N{\rYUANWEN}I can't say I have, Sheriff.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.06,0:05:15.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,一个人出生 然后某天\N{\rYUANWEN}You're born, and one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.11,0:05:17.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这个人死去\N{\rYUANWEN}- ...you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.24,0:05:21.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,仅此而已\N{\rYUANWEN}That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.28,0:05:25.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,祝你一天愉快\N{\rYUANWEN}I wish you a good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.25,0:05:37.42,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好 这个镇子归我们接管了\N{\rYUANWEN}AlI right. We're takin over the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.42,0:05:40.21,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们会恢复林肯的法律和秩序\N{\rYUANWEN}We're gonna restore law and order in Lincoln,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.22,0:05:43.63,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但要先干掉浩世才行\N{\rYUANWEN}but we have to take out The House to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.64,0:05:46.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们要沿着主街进发\N{\rYUANWEN}We're gonna ride in hard through Main Street,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.18,0:05:47.97,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,然后兵分三路\N{\rYUANWEN}splitting into three smaller groups
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.97,0:05:49.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,一路拿下沃特利酒店\N{\rYUANWEN}to take the Wortley Hotel,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.93,0:05:51.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,一路拿下汤斯顿商行\N{\rYUANWEN}the Tunstall Store.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.60,0:05:54.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,一路负责胡安和墨西哥分队 你们负责镇中心\N{\rYUANWEN}Juan and the Mexicans, you'll take the downtown area.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.19,0:05:56.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,抢占以下战略位置 就能对浩世集团形成夹击\N{\rYUANWEN}From these strategic positions, I believe we can cut off
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.19,0:05:58.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,把他们赶出镇子\N{\rYUANWEN}the house and drive'em out,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.40,0:06:00.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,解放林肯的人民\N{\rYUANWEN}liberating the people of Lincoln
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.28,0:06:03.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,把这里变成净土\N{\rYUANWEN}and makin' the town safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.45,0:06:05.66,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们只要当心加勒特治安官就行\N{\rYUANWEN}We just have to watch for Sheriff Garrett.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.66,0:06:07.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他那边什么消息\N{\rYUANWEN}I don't have a read on him yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:09.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们只知道 他把几个手下借给了杰西\N{\rYUANWEN}Yeah, well we do know that he's lent Jesse
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.37,0:06:11.33,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们正在全县范围内\N{\rYUANWEN}a couple of his deputies, and they're
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.33,0:06:13.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,搜寻我们\N{\rYUANWEN}searching the county for us right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.37,0:06:15.42,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以我们更要转战下一个城镇\N{\rYUANWEN}That's another reason for moving into town now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.42,0:06:17.50,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好的 让我们开始吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Right. Let's get to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.30,0:06:22.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们上\N{\rYUANWEN}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.14,0:06:28.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,枪战开始时一定要保持警惕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.77,0:06:33.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我觉得他们会把我们逼到镇广场
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.27,0:06:37.06,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你派几个人过来\N{\rYUANWEN}So have a few of your men come through
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.06,0:06:38.44,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,从山坡上包抄他们\N{\rYUANWEN}and flank 'em from the hillside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.11,0:06:41.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好的比利别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.28,0:06:44.03,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-照顾好自己 朋友 -你也是 我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.39,0:07:09.64,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,大家各就各位 快\N{\rYUANWEN}Everyone to your positions. Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.64,0:07:11.51,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-乔治 去屋顶 -好的\N{\rYUANWEN}George, take the roof. On it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.44,0:07:18.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,到底是怎么回事\N{\rYUANWEN}What the hell's goin'on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.61,0:07:20.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,对不起 山姆\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm sorry, Sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.40,0:07:23.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们需要暂时接管你的酒店\N{\rYUANWEN}We're talking over your hotel for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.28,0:07:24.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,保护好他们 小子们\N{\rYUANWEN}Keep'em safe, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.87,0:07:34.54,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,威尔逊法官发给国会议员的\N{\rYUANWEN}What happened with the letter
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.54,0:07:36.62,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那封信情况如何了\N{\rYUANWEN}that Judge Wilson sent to the congressman?
