Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.49,0:29:43.87,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,代表执法机关来出手干预呢\N{\rYUANWEN}on behalf of the forces of law and order?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.46,0:29:50.71,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不 加勒特治安官\N{\rYUANWEN}No, Sheriff Garrett.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.71,0:29:53.54,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,其实 我在这里的职责\N{\rYUANWEN}You see, my job here
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.54,0:29:57.46,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,就是不断权衡 如果军队参予到公民社会中\N{\rYUANWEN}is always to weigh out the advantages and disadvantages
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.46,0:30:01.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,会带来哪些利弊\N{\rYUANWEN}of involving the army in civil society.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.89,0:30:06.01,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但我们一旦如此 就会招来\N{\rYUANWEN}And when we do, we often earn the ill- will
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.01,0:30:08.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,大家的反感 治安官\N{\rYUANWEN}of the population, and that, Sheriff.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.48,0:30:13.56,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以说 这个问题很棘手\N{\rYUANWEN}is a matter of great consideration.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.49,0:30:28.66,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我告诉你 你要是不马上插手\N{\rYUANWEN}Let me tell you that unless you interfere right away,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.66,0:30:31.83,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,林肯街上将会血流成河\N{\rYUANWEN}there will be a massacre on the streets of Lincoln.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.83,0:30:34.46,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你不觉得这会给你和你军队的形象\N{\rYUANWEN}Don't you think that will earn you and the Army
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.46,0:30:36.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,扳回一局吗\N{\rYUANWEN}the ill- will of the people?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.11,0:30:58.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,祝你晚上愉快\N{\rYUANWEN}I wish you a good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.05,0:31:19.42,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,贝克维斯\N{\rYUANWEN}Beckwith!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.67,0:31:22.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-贝克维斯 -在\N{\rYUANWEN}Beckwith? - Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.84,0:31:25.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-油 -钉死了\N{\rYUANWEN}Oil! - Hammer it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.55,0:31:29.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,大家快点\N{\rYUANWEN}Let's go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.75,0:31:55.83,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我会为你祈祷的 比利\N{\rYUANWEN}I'|l pray for you, Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.59,0:32:01.05,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们决不投降\N{\rYUANWEN}We must never surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.05,0:32:02.55,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我现在相信了\N{\rYUANWEN}I believe that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.18,0:32:08.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们是在为事业而战\N{\rYUANWEN}We're fighting for a good cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.10,0:32:09.97,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,一项崇高的事业\N{\rYUANWEN}A noble cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.64,0:32:14.02,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,愿上帝赐予你胜利\N{\rYUANWEN}May God give you the victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.19,0:32:18.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\rYUANWEN}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.98,0:32:21.02,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,真希望能借你吉言\N{\rYUANWEN}I do hope you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.19,0:32:25.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以\N{\rYUANWEN}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.78,0:32:28.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你们要怎么做\N{\rYUANWEN}What are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.32,0:32:30.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你觉得管理者真有那么强吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Do you think the Regulators
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.74,0:32:32.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,能跑到这里打我们\N{\rYUANWEN}are strong enough to attack us here?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.71,0:32:35.66,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,没错 他们很强\N{\rYUANWEN}Yeah, they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.12,0:32:39.29,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那你有何对策\N{\rYUANWEN}Then what are ya gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.18,0:32:48.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,莱利 稳住\N{\rYUANWEN}Riley, steady.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.93,0:32:53.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我觉得你们最好来外面看看\N{\rYUANWEN}I reckon you boys should take a look outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.78,0:33:52.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,真厉害 加勒特治安官 真厉害\N{\rYUANWEN}Good man, Sheriff Garrett. Good man!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.39,0:34:12.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,达德利上校\N{\rYUANWEN}Colonel Dudley.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.18,0:34:18.64,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,达德利上校\N{\rYUANWEN}Colonel Dudley.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.73,0:34:25.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\rYUANWEN}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.78,0:34:27.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你来得正是时候\N{\rYUANWEN}You came just in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.90,0:34:29.36,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,全体 立正\N{\rYUANWEN}Company, halt!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.36,0:34:31.78,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,别担心 治安官 这是我们职责所在\N{\rYUANWEN}It's all right, Sheriff. Just doing our duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.33,0:34:38.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,治安官\N{\rYUANWEN}Sheriff.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.41,0:34:42.33,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你想逮捕哪些人来着\N{\rYUANWEN}Which men do you want arrested, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.46,0:34:47.71,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我想逮捕他们全部\N{\rYUANWEN}I want the whole damn business.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.01,0:34:55.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,加勒特治安官 我把话说清楚\N{\rYUANWEN}Sheriff Garrett, let me be perfectly clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.01,0:35:01.02,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我今天到林肯来 并不是要帮你们\N{\rYUANWEN}I did not come to Lincoln today to assist you in any way.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.15,0:35:06.23,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我是来确保妇女和儿童安全的\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm here to ensure the safety of the women and children.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.23,0:35:09.44,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,男人的事 就让男人自己解决\N{\rYUANWEN}The men can take care of themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.44,0:35:12.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但我强调一下 要是有任何人\N{\rYUANWEN}But if anyone, and I stress anyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.28,0:35:13.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,朝我的军队开火\N{\rYUANWEN}fires upon my company,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.99,0:35:17.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我会马上还击 明白吗\N{\rYUANWEN}I will return fire immediately. Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.24,0:35:21.08,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,达德利上校 我是亚历山大·麦克斯文\N{\rYUANWEN}Colonel Dudley, I am Alexander McSween.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.08,0:35:23.87,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我是管理者的律师\N{\rYUANWEN}I act as attorney for the Regulators,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.87,0:35:26.08,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,而管理者 是一群致力于终结林肯县的\N{\rYUANWEN}those who are fighting for an end to corruption
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.08,0:35:28.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,腐败而斗争的人 看到您的部队\N{\rYUANWEN}here in Lincoln. While I am gratified
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.09,0:35:30.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,愿意保持中立 我不胜感激\N{\rYUANWEN}that your troopers will remain neutral,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.30,0:35:33.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我必须指出 在你的支持者中\N{\rYUANWEN}I must point out that among those supporting you
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.30,0:35:36.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,有几人被指控谋杀了约翰·汤斯顿\N{\rYUANWEN}are several men charged with the murder of John Tunstall
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.22,0:35:38.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我有将其就地抓获的逮捕令\N{\rYUANWEN}and for whose immediate arrest I carry warrants,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.89,0:35:40.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,由法官约翰·威尔逊亲自签署\N{\rYUANWEN}signed by a Judge John Wilson.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.27,0:35:42.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我还有抓捕布雷迪治安官谋杀案\N{\rYUANWEN}And I have warrants for the arrest
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.43,0:35:46.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,凶手的逮捕令呢\N{\rYUANWEN}of those responsible for the murder of Sheriff Brady.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.40,0:35:48.86,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,有些凶手就站你面前 麦克斯文先生\N{\rYUANWEN}Some of whom are standing right over there, Mr. McSween.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.07,0:35:54.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,先生们 我今天不是要逮捕谁\N{\rYUANWEN}Gentlemen, I am not here to arrest anyone today.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.15,0:35:56.36,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,而是来恢复和平的\N{\rYUANWEN}I came here to restore the peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.16,0:36:02.16,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我命令所有人马上回家\N{\rYUANWEN}I am ordering all of you to go home, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.16,0:36:03.96,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,立即离开\N{\rYUANWEN}Leave immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.96,0:36:07.00,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这个城镇将实行无限制宵禁\N{\rYUANWEN}This town is under permanent curfew.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.00,0:36:10.46,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,任何人未经允许\N{\rYUANWEN}Find anybody out on the streets past hours
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.46,0:36:13.01,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,在街上逗留超过几小时\N{\rYUANWEN}without permission or a damn good reason
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.01,0:36:16.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,就会被捕 都明白么\N{\rYUANWEN}will be arrested. Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.18,0:36:17.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,清楚吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.51,0:36:20.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-副队呢 -明白\N{\rYUANWEN}Lieutenant? - Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.10,0:36:29.44,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,骑兵 封锁城南\N{\rYUANWEN}Cavalry, cordon to the south.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.44,0:36:32.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,步兵小心疏散平民\N{\rYUANWEN}Infantry, let's clear the civilians, gently.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.39,0:37:08.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好了 让我们为内森·达德利上校\N{\rYUANWEN}AlI right, let's raise a glass to Colonel Nathan Dudley
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.85,0:37:10.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,和美国骑兵干一杯\N{\rYUANWEN}and the U. S. Cavalry.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.27,0:37:11.56,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,喝吧 小子们\N{\rYUANWEN}Let's go, boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.11,0:37:14.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,别忘了帕特·加勒特\N{\rYUANWEN}And don't forget Pat Garrett.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.90,0:37:17.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他也是个好人 为帕特·加勒特治安官干一杯\N{\rYUANWEN}He's a good man. Raise a glass to Sheriff Pat Garrett.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.08,0:37:29.00,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这是你的\N{\rYUANWEN}That's yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.55,0:37:35.05,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你有什么想说的吗\N{\rYUANWEN}So what do you gotta say for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.59,0:37:38.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你什么意思\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, what do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.22,0:37:39.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,问我什么意思\N{\rYUANWEN}What do I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.35,0:37:45.14,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,帕特·加勒特救了你一次\N{\rYUANWEN}Pat Garrett just about saved your ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.94,0:37:51.02,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,而你连个屁都没放\N{\rYUANWEN}You personally have done jack shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.02,0:37:52.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这就是我的意思\N{\rYUANWEN}That's what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.21,0:38:12.42,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-怎么样 -他们在墨菲商行\N{\rYUANWEN}Well? - They've put up their tents
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.42,0:38:14.29,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,南边的空地中搭了个帐篷\N{\rYUANWEN}in a field just below Murphy's store.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.29,0:38:17.21,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们赢了 墨菲和莱利 他们赢了\N{\rYUANWEN}They've won. Murphy and Riley. They've won.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.21,0:38:20.55,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,并没有赢 达德利上校才是这个国家真正的法律\N{\rYUANWEN}No, they haven't. Colonel Dudley is the real law in this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.55,0:38:22.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们跟他解释清楚就行\N{\rYUANWEN}And when we explain to him- -
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.14,0:38:25.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这不会有啥区别的 麦克斯文太太\N{\rYUANWEN}It won't make any difference, Mrs. McSween.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.10,0:38:26.64,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,上校发誓说 他不会偏袒任何一方\N{\rYUANWEN}The Colonel swore he wasn't taking sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.64,0:38:28.64,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他只是来恢复和平的\N{\rYUANWEN}He's only here to restore the peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.64,0:38:29.52,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,也不知道出什么事了\N{\rYUANWEN}I don't know what happened. I didn't think
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.52,0:38:30.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,军队都要介入降维打击\N{\rYUANWEN}the army was gonna get involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.98,0:38:32.48,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们不应该被牵进来的\N{\rYUANWEN}They're not supposed to get involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.48,0:38:33.56,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,真是出乎所有人意料\N{\rYUANWEN}No one saw this comin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.69,0:38:37.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我没想到会这样\N{\rYUANWEN}I didn't see this comin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.28,0:38:42.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我马上回来\N{\rYUANWEN}I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.32,0:38:45.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,比利\N{\rYUANWEN}Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.61,0:40:02.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,杰西在哪儿\N{\rYUANWEN}Where's Jesse?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.69,0:40:04.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不知道 怎么了\N{\rYUANWEN}I don't know. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.11,0:40:06.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,马上离开 快点\N{\rYUANWEN}Leave. Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.24,0:40:08.32,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们得把你我二人的计划定好 眼下就是机会\N{\rYUANWEN}We need to make plans. Now's our chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.33,0:40:09.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\rYUANWEN}For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.37,0:40:12.25,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好做出新的行动\N{\rYUANWEN}To make new moves!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.83,0:40:17.42,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-我会找到他的 莱利先生 -去找吧\N{\rYUANWEN}- I'll find him, Mr. Riley. - Do.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.55,0:41:08.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你好啊 比利\N{\rYUANWEN}Hello, Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.72,0:41:11.80,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,帕特\N{\rYUANWEN}Pat.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.56,0:41:15.35,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,很高兴见到你\N{\rYUANWEN}It's good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.73,0:41:17.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,真的吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.90,0:41:25.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,听着 我不想让你觉得\N{\rYUANWEN}Look, I don't want you to think
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.40,0:41:27.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们两方是对垒关系\N{\rYUANWEN}that we're on opposite sides here.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.24,0:41:30.36,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,因为我们不是\N{\rYUANWEN}Because we're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.41,0:41:32.78,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我想要你想要的东西\N{\rYUANWEN}I want what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.78,0:41:34.79,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,怎么 你也想要正义\N{\rYUANWEN}Oh, you want justice too?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.79,0:41:36.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我当然想要正义了\N{\rYUANWEN}Of course I want justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.83,0:41:41.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你想要结束浩世 还是结束指环王\N{\rYUANWEN}You want the end of the House? The end of the Rings?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.59,0:41:44.67,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这我控制不了 比利 我只是治安官\N{\rYUANWEN}I can't control that, Billy. I'm just the sheriff.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.67,0:41:46.51,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,作为治安官\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, as just the sheriff,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.51,0:41:48.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你更应该在这件事上保持中立\N{\rYUANWEN}I presume you're gonna stay neutral in this whole business
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.59,0:41:50.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,而不是总偏袒站错队的浩世\N{\rYUANWEN}and not pick sides with the House.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.22,0:41:52.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,比利 事情比这复杂多了\N{\rYUANWEN}Billy, it is so much more complicated than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.85,0:41:54.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,去他妈的\N{\rYUANWEN}The fuck it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.26,0:41:56.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你不能与体制抗争\N{\rYUANWEN}You can't fight the system.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.77,0:41:58.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这话说的对味了\N{\rYUANWEN}And now we're talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.73,0:42:02.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,如果没有法律 那就成了无政府\N{\rYUANWEN}If there's no law, there's only anarchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.31,0:42:03.81,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这对谁都没有好处\N{\rYUANWEN}And that is in no one's interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.82,0:42:05.48,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,知道吗 我越来越觉得他是在背台词了\N{\rYUANWEN}You know, that sounds like it's right outta their handbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.48,0:42:06.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,比利\N{\rYUANWEN}Billy...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.87,0:42:17.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你必须放弃\N{\rYUANWEN}You have to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.92,0:42:23.50,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你赢不了的\N{\rYUANWEN}You can't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.50,0:42:25.67,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你什么时候才能明白 这对我来说不是游戏\N{\rYUANWEN}When are you gonna learn this ain't a game for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.67,0:42:27.76,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不在乎输赢\N{\rYUANWEN}I don't care about winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.42,0:42:31.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我关心的只是 长久以来\N{\rYUANWEN}All I care about is that for too long,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.59,0:42:33.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,圣达菲的几个腐败混蛋\N{\rYUANWEN}a few corrupt assholes in Santa Fe,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.68,0:42:36.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,比如阿克塞尔和卡特隆\N{\rYUANWEN}like Axtell and Catron,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.39,0:42:38.52,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,掌控中林肯的一切\N{\rYUANWEN}been pullin' all the strings down here in Lincoln,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.52,0:42:41.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,把这些可怜人榨干\N{\rYUANWEN}bleedin'these poor people dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.19,0:42:42.56,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,只要有任何人站出来\N{\rYUANWEN}And if they speak up, if anyone speaks up,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.56,0:42:44.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们都会保持沉默\N{\rYUANWEN}they're silenced.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.40,0:42:47.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,要是学不会沉默 他们就会被暗杀\N{\rYUANWEN}And if they can't be silenced, well, then, they're killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.61,0:42:52.66,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们只想改变这一点 帕特\N{\rYUANWEN}We're just tryin' to change it, Pat.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.58,0:42:57.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但我们需要你的帮助\N{\rYUANWEN}But we need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.71,0:43:04.79,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你曾被授予过徽章 说明你有这个能力\N{\rYUANWEN}You have been given a badge. You have the power.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.55,0:43:11.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,利用它吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Use it.
